{"tid":2366353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老味 香港寬頻事隔6日改口 首認按《國安法》封「香港編年史」網站","createTime":"2021-01-14T12:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T16:10:04.000Z","uid":288699,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18d6daf31f77126c2d7967d0b783f13cdb3dec21","tid":2366353,"uid":288699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:10:35.000Z","msg":"節錄<br />\n港人無法連接網站「香港編年史」已經一周，但一直只得傳媒引述消息指警方引用《國安法》封鎖網站，消息今日終獲確認。一直連接到網站、6日前仍稱沒有封鎖的香港寬頻，今日承認昨日下午起已按照《國安法》要求「停止連線至有關網站」，是首次有網絡供應商承認根據《國安法》封鎖網站。《蘋果》正向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/MTWLC2Y2GRDPHMMRRMWPFTYSKE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2FMTWLC2Y2GRDPHMMRRMWPFTYSKE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=313bff2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2FMTWLC2Y2GRDPHMMRRMWPFTYSKE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram&h=e51dfce9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/MTWLC2Y2GRDPHMMRRMWPFTYSKE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=telegram</a>"},{"pid":"3bfda821393c38142375bb0a8a042c3b84228ece","tid":2366353,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb846f75c54f891864886fdd78e51aefc1b23fb","tid":2366353,"uid":288699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmo